{"tid":1657301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑警催淚彈庫存快耗盡  西方國家拒供應   承認「有向中國購入」","createTime":"2019-10-16T04:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T14:34:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f2d5d3463a071712f817a88b8eda96abf7478eba","tid":1657301,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:35:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2943907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2943907&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVl8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=e914dcc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2943907&h=a544fec1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2943907</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpzGi4WF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpzGi4WF.jpg&h=0e2ef4f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港反送中過去4個月期間，港警發射數千催淚彈壓制示威者，昨（11）日傳出催淚彈庫存將耗盡，港警會開始使用中國製催淚彈，對此，港警行動部高級警司汪威遜昨日下午在例行記者會上承認<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「現在有向中國購入彈藥」</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n因民間組織請願歐美國家停止供應催淚彈給港府，昨日傳出港警現時催淚彈庫存短缺，打算使用中國製品作為替代，據《立場新聞》 報導，汪威遜昨日在記者會上承認「現在有向中國購入彈藥」，不過，他說，並非不斷購買新彈藥，也不是指定要於某個國家及地區引入彈藥，而是透過既定機制，了解世界各地有哪些生產商可以滿足警方的彈藥需求。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有記者詢問中國製與之前從英國引入的催淚彈效果是否不同，對示威者的傷害是否更大，汪威遜回應，與現時引入的彈藥效果相同；不過，有消息指出，中國製催淚彈爆發時間較外國貨快0.3秒，發射後1.2秒就會爆發。"},{"pid":"2997e154f018f22a5bca83a1e14cc3c2da050dae","tid":1657301,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:35:19.000Z","msg":"1020 到時見!<br />\n<br />\n等我為大家回憶下決定1020去定唔去[2]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657270</a>"},{"pid":"f2f5b7726cffed7d1b10cd7f34889ad9eb87b175","tid":1657301,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:35:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1QUeo.jpg&h=564aedde&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4b8fd19fa9dfc6d9e1c36c9fe6abf277c5a07b2a","tid":1657301,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:35:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2943213\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2943213&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVl8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=5fa6e290\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2943213&h=7d81b0e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2943213</a><br />\n<br />\n綜合港媒報導，有消息人士透露，香港警方的催淚彈庫存已經快要用完，將使用中國製的催淚瓦斯作為替代，中國製的催淚瓦斯為570克的「Jing An」KF-302-20 CS Grenade，重量較輕，爆炸時間較短，施放後會在1.2秒內爆炸，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">效果持續15至25秒</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，過去4個月內，香港警方發射數千發進口催淚彈，有民主組織請願歐美停止供應，如今香港警方尋求中國製品作為替代。<br />\n<br />\n這起消息在國外論壇引起討論，有網友稱「中國製品，可能會在丟出前自行爆炸」，也有人說「最討厭的是，這些催淚彈的資金，技術上來說包含了抗爭者繳納的稅金」。"},{"pid":"ecdd6f940ebd0c5dd683052a983b7963597ae5bf","tid":1657301,"uid":268481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:37:25.000Z","msg":"我印象中有1.5-3萬粒架<br />\n邊會咁快用哂"},{"pid":"8909052267ef7daf77add95d13e3c7c82b5b9763","tid":1657301,"uid":327462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ecdd6f940ebd0c5dd683052a983b7963597ae5bf","tid":1657301,"uid":268481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:37:25.000Z","msg":"我印象中有1.5-3萬粒架<br />\n邊會咁快用哂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:37:58.000Z","msg":"可能支那催淚彈加左料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e387d4480a549a7322c0ba2d98474768dbe952da","tid":1657301,"uid":225977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ecdd6f940ebd0c5dd683052a983b7963597ae5bf","tid":1657301